    <Teaser>Adds Remilia Scarlet to the game.</Teaser>
    <Description>Adds Remilia Scarlet of the Scarlet Estate from the Touhou Project games as a playable civilization.

Big thanks to Tetraoxygen for providing the art!

[h1][b]----------Civilization Info[/b][/h1]

[b]UA - Scarlet Mist[/b]: +1 XP per turn for Units in owned territory, up to Level 4. Reduces Culture cost of acquiring new tiles by 25%.

[b]UU - Fairy Maid[/b]: Replaces the worker. +25% work rate, ignores terrain cost.

[b]UB - Magic Library[/b]: Replaces the library. +1 Science for every 2 Citizens, +1 Happiness, +1 Food from Lake tiles. (Expansion only: an additional +2 Culture from Lake tiles)

